Yoko Ono said she was 'very saddened' by news of Cynthia Lennon's death . 
 She praised Cynthia, 75, as a 'great person' with a 'strong zest for life'Cynthia Lennon, nee Powell, married John Lennon after they met at college . 
 She is the mother of the musician's son Julian Lennon, who is now aged 51 . 
 But the couple divorced in 1968 after Lennon left her for artist Yoko Ono . 
 